===Noun===
'''[[present]] [[participle]]'''

# {{grammar}}: A [[verb]] form that indicates an ongoing action or state in the present and which functions as an [[adjective]]. In English, the present participle takes the suffix ''[[-ing]]'' and is preceded by a form of the verb ''to [[be]]'' to make the [[progressive tense]]s of a verb.

